column2: select  s.specobjid, s.bestobjid, s.firstrelease, s.survey, s.sourcetype, s.class,  gal.ra, gal.raErr, gal.dec, gal.decErr, s.z, s.zErr,  gal.modelMag_g, gal.modelMag_r, gal.modelMag_i, gal.psfMag_g,  gal.petroMag_r, gal.petroR5#_r INTO mydb.LRG_CUT3 FROM Galaxy as gal   JOIN specobj as s on s.bestobjid = gal.objid WHERE (flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)    | dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)    | dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) > #    and (flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)    | dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)    | dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) != dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)    and (flags & (dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)    | dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) = #    and (gal.petroMag_r > # and gal.g > # and gal.r > # and gal.i > #)    and ((gal.petroMag_r-gal.extinction_r < #)     and ((gal.petroMag_r - gal.extinction_r) < (# + (# * (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r) + # * (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i) - # * #)/#))     and (ABS(gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i - (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r)/# - #) < #)     and ((gal.petroMag_r - gal.extinction_r + # * LOG1#(# * # * gal.petroR5#_r * gal.petroR5#_r)) < #))   or ((gal.petroMag_r - gal.extinction_r < #)     and ((gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i - (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r)/# - #) > (# - (gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r)/#))     and ((gal.dered_g - gal.dered_r) > (# + # * (gal.dered_r - gal.dered_i)))     and ((gal.petroMag_r - gal.extinction_r + # * LOG1#(# * # * gal.petroR5#_r * gal.petroR5#_r)) < #))
